    dc:description "Figure 9. Sporothrix cryptarchum sp. nov. (CBS 147934) a ascoma b ascomatal base c, d ostiolar hyphae e ascospores f asci g conidiogenous cell with an inflated cluster of denticles at the apex h conidia i globose conidia arising on long conidiophore j globose conidia arising directly from hyphae k fourteen-day-old culture on MEA. Scale bars: 100 μm (a), 25 μm (b-d), 10 μm (e), 25 μm (f, g), 10 μm (h, i), 5 μm (j)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/574237" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

